```python
def orthogonalize(z_c, z_p, z_s, U_c, U_p, U_s):
    z_c_orth = z_c - U_p @ (U_p.T @ z_c) - U_s @ (U_s.T @ z_c)
    z_p_orth = z_p - U_c @ (U_c.T @ z_p) - U_s @ (U_s.T @ z_p)
    z_s_orth = z_s - U_c @ (U_c.T @ z_s) - U_p @ (U_p.T @ z_s)
    return z_c_orth, z_p_orth, z_s_orth
```

