C.4 Computational Graph

The forward pass at inference time for a single 20ms chunk:

```
Audio Chunk (320 samples) 
    → Speech Encoder (Conv stack) 
    → 1024-dim embedding
    → Concatenate with text/prompt embeddings (if any)
    → LDVS Step:
        → Layer 1: SSM → Attention (if layer%2==0) → Ortho (if layer%2==0) → LN → Residual
        → ...
        → Layer 10
    → Latent state z_t
    → CTC Head → Text output (streaming)
    → Predictive Head → Future latents (cached)
    → (If turn boundary) LSR Reset
```

